ADDITIONAL TERMS: RESPONSIBLE USE & DISCLAIMER
===========================================

1. Intended Purpose  
   This repository is provided to help administrators block access to adult / NSFW
   domains using network filtering tools such as Pi-hole. It is meant for lawful,
   voluntary content filtering, parental control, and organizational network
   administration.

